<paragraph id="C8639966FFFB2C0CF3D6FCD001909D41" blockId="1.[113,776,573,858]" box="[136,725,779,800]" pageId="1" pageNumber="236">Habitat in bracteas Cirsii spinosissimi in regio alpina, Helvetia.</paragraph>
